        "timestamp": "2018-07-06 13:45:10.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nHi Praveen,\n\nYes I agree with Jorge. It would also be useful to see how this change fits in with ONAP in general and with the Policy Framework in particular.\n\nThanks",
